txt.en: You have been tasked with removing the enemies encamped at the tower ruins of Sutwarden.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Radhril for your reward!

'Would you accompany me on a mission, [placeholder]?

'The Free Peoples in the Wildwood have been unable to regain control of the watch-tower ruins of Sutwarden. Those who control the tower have a vantage point to view all of the Wildwood and the Bree-fields.

'If the Wildwood and the Bree-fields are to ever again be safe, the tower of Sutwarden must be reclaimed.'
Complete Mission: The Menace of Sutwarden

The old Arnorian watch-tower of Sutwarden has attracted many foes of the Free Peoples, who wish to spy upon the Bree-fields.\n\nYour mission is to remove the enemies encamped at the tower ruins of Sutwarden.
You may be ambushed after completing your objective.
Your mission is to remove the enemies encamped at the tower ruins of Sutwarden.\n\nSpeak to Radhril.

'We have done well, [placeholder]. With Sutwarden once again under control of the Free Peoples, both the Bree-fields and the Wildwood are much safer. I am certain the Free Peoples will thank us for our efforts.'
